item.title: How do i start up MoparScape(Like joining a server or something like that)
item.dc:creator: @archerer98 Archer
item.description:
@archerer98 wrote:

download moparscape client 3.2 in the download section.once its downloaded type in a username and pass and for the ip go to the "help"tab at the top of the client and choose “server status” and pick a online server you want to join then type the ip of that server where it asks for the ip.
